data.title: DeFi & L1L2 Weekly — 🔒 Vitalik Buterin unveiled Ethereum privacy toolkit and wallet framework, Kohaku
data.description: Vitalik unveiled Ethereum privacy framework, Kohaku. EVM-compatible L1 Monad and decentralised Ethereum L2 Aztec launched. HSBC will expand tokenised deposits to the US and UAE in H1 2026.
